2. DPDP COMPLIANCE ADDENDUM: This Software is designed for compliance with the
Digital Personal Data Protection Act 2023 (India). Any deployment must ensure:
   a) Data residency within India (§8(2)(a))
   b) Privacy budget ε ≤ 9.5 (§9(4))
   c) Explicit consent mechanisms (§11(3))
   d) Breach notification within 72 hours (§25)
   e) Sovereign hosting on NIC Cloud India (§7(1))

3. BYZANTINE FAULT TOLERANCE: This Software includes Byzantine fault tolerance
mechanisms. Any production deployment must maintain the geometric median
aggregation and reputation-based weighting systems.

