Ghost Protocol Privacy Notice:

This Software implements differential privacy mechanisms for protecting
personal medical data. The privacy budget (ε) is tracked in real-time and
automatically halts training when approaching the DPDP-mandated limit of 9.5.

By using this Software, you acknowledge your responsibility to:
- Maintain privacy budget compliance
- Implement proper consent mechanisms
- Ensure data residency requirements
- Report any privacy breaches immediately

For questions about DPDP compliance, contact: compliance@ghost-protocol.ai